{"tid":1649480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府強烈譴責蒙面暴徒暴力行為","createTime":"2019-10-12T16:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T16:41:04.000Z","uid":184755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09b8a135d3f5853bb2979764159ef156681bbfb4","tid":1649480,"uid":184755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"2019年10月12日<br />\n<br />\n政府發表聲明，對蒙面暴徒破壞社會安寧、威脅市民安全的行為予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，今日示威者在九龍區多處堵塞道路，嚴重阻塞交通。蒙面暴徒趁機大肆破壞政府設施、港鐵站及多間暴徒選定的銀行和商舖，更有人縱火及在運作中的港鐵站內投擲汽油彈，行為極為危險。<br />\n<br />\n政府呼籲市民與暴徒割席，與政府共同努力回覆社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZDSMnX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZDSMnX.jpg&h=036f0204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRzVJ9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRzVJ9D.jpg&h=aa0fb8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w16H8Bi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw16H8Bi.jpg&h=d388a064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nHzbhuE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnHzbhuE.png&h=57576c52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/er4eZHZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fer4eZHZ.png&h=c3c3fbdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaV2o9F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaV2o9F.jpg&h=e235fa5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uf5hXuG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuf5hXuG.png&h=bdcbd9d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe3331e472fd5f777e185adf95fff62fa0f704c1","tid":1649480,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"只會譴責<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-li